==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shrewish
<hw>Shrew"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>having the qualities
of a shrew; having a scolding disposition; froward; peevish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My wife is <qex>shrewish</qex> when I keep not hours.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Shrew"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Shrew"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shrewmouse</ent>⟦br⟧
